<p><a name="Water_as_a_natural_resource" id="Water_as_a_natural_resource"></a></p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline">Water as a natural resource</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFGleick">Gleick, Peter H.. <i>The World's Water: The Biennial Report on Freshwater Resources</i>. Washington: Island Press.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+World%27s+Water%3A+The+Biennial+Report+on+Freshwater+Resources&amp;rft.aulast=Gleick&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter+H.&amp;rft.au=Gleick%2C+Peter+H.&amp;rft.place=Washington&amp;rft.pub=Island+Press&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Water"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (November 10, 2006)| ISBN-13: 9781597261050]</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFPostel1997.2C_second_edition">Postel, Sandra (1997, second edition). <i>Last Oasis: Facing Water Scarcity</i>. New York: Norton Press.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Last+Oasis%3A+Facing+Water+Scarcity&amp;rft.aulast=Postel&amp;rft.aufirst=Sandra&amp;rft.au=Postel%2C+Sandra&amp;rft.date=1997%2C+second+edition&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Norton+Press&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Water"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
